snippet.textDisplay: AD challenged Lebron to play DEFENSE? So...how come the Lakers can't win a game without Lebron? And how come the Clippers can't win a game without Kawhi? Honestly, right now, I'm starting to give Nick Nurse a helluva lot of credit for that Toronto Raptors title. Ofcourse Kawhi was a big part of that, but, that coaching hasn't missed a step without Kawhi...so, I mean, you gotta give them boys in Toronto maad credit.
